channel.title: Sketchup Pro 6
channel.description: Does anyone know where I can get the serial for Sketchup Pro 6? The limits of what the free version can do just does not seem to be enough such as sometimes I need to export the .skp files as a different format but that is not possible without buying it. Also the price is just a little over the top. If someone could please find some valid serials that would be great! Thanks
